title: (Thurs Full) What Went Down At Bobby’s House Last Night + Lunchbox Burns the Haunted Doll + We Spin the Wheel of Anime
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) What Went Down At Bobby’s House Last Night + Lunchbox Burns the Haunted Doll + We Spin the Wheel of Anime
description:
Bobby reveals what went down at his house that had him on edge. He also reveals what his dog is doing now that’s scaring the crap out of him. We get the final update on Lunchbox and the Haunted Crying Boy Doll.  We spin the wall of Anime and the loser has to watch a show on Netflix.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
